<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.6.6">
<l>iṉavēymalai yēntiṉēṉ yāṉē yeṉṉu miṉavēṟukaḷ ceṟṟēṉum yāṉē yeṉṉu</l>
<l>miṉavāṉkaṉṟu mēyttēṉum yāṉē yeṉṉu miṉavānirai kāttēṉum yāṉē yeṉṉu</l>
<l>miṉavāyar talaivaṉum yāṉē yeṉṉu miṉattēvar talaivaṉvan tēṟak kolō</l>
<l>viṉavēṟkaṇ ṇallīrk kivaiyeṉ collukē ṉiṉavēṟ kaṇṇi yeṉmaka ḷuṟṟaṉavē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>“I lifted the moutain with bamboo in groups”, she says,</l>
	<l>“and I am the one who restrained the bulls in groups”, she says,</l>
<l>“and I am the one who let the calves of the cows in a herd graze”, she says,</l>
	<l>“and I am the one who guarded the cow herd in a group”, she says,</l>
<l>“and I [am] the head-man of the cowherds in a group”, she says,</l>
	<l>while the head-man of the gods in a group settles in [her]?</l>
<l>Why will I say these [words] to you good ones with spear eyes in groups,</l>
	<l>[words] suffered by my daughter with spear eyes in groups?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
